</b></p>
<p><b>  Report of the Secretary-General 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Corrigendum 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Paragraph 76 
</b></p>
<p>The first sentence <i>should read</i> 
</p>
<p>Internal alignment with the Guiding Principles by the United Nations system should be 
</p>
<p>grounded in the responsibility to avoid causing or contributing to human rights abuses, or 
</p>
<p>being involved with such abuse through relationships with business entities.  
